"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.4\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.4</span> 标题：宫殿（palace）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：אַרְמוֹן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：’armon)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:18\">1KI 16:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:25\">2KI 15:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:19\">2CH 36:19</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：בִּירָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：birah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:1\">1CH 29:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:19\">1CH 29:19</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：בַּיִת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：bayith)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:15\">GEN 12:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:17\">GEN 12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:40\">GEN 41:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:2\">GEN 45:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:8\">GEN 45:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:16\">GEN 45:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:14\">GEN 47:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:4\">GEN 50:4</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：בַּיִת מֶלֶךְ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：beyth (ha)melek)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:2\">2SA 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:8\">2SA 11:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:9\">2SA 11:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:35\">2SA 15:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:1\">1KI 9:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:10\">1KI 9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:12\">1KI 10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:26\">1KI 14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:27\">1KI 14:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:18\">1KI 15:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:18\">1KI 16:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:18\">1KI 16:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:5\">2KI 11:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:16\">2KI 11:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:19\">2KI 11:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:20\">2KI 11:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:19\">2KI 12:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:14\">2KI 14:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:25\">2KI 15:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:8\">2KI 16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:15\">2KI 18:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:13\">2KI 24:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:9\">2KI 25:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:11\">2CH 7:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:11\">2CH 8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:11\">2CH 9:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:10\">2CH 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:2\">2CH 16:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:17\">2CH 21:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr23:5\">2CH 23:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr23:15\">2CH 23:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr23:20\">2CH 23:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:24\">2CH 25:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:21\">2CH 28:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:25\">NEH 3:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:8\">EST 2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:9\">EST 2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:13\">EST 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:13\">EST 4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth5:1\">EST 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth5:1\">EST 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth6:4\">EST 6:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:4\">EST 9:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer19:13\">JER 19:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer21:11\">JER 21:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:1\">JER 22:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:10\">JER 26:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:18\">JER 27:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:21\">JER 27:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:2\">JER 32:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:4\">JER 33:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer36:12\">JER 36:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:7\">JER 38:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:8\">JER 38:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:11\">JER 38:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:22\">JER 38:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer39:8\">JER 39:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:13\">JER 52:13</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：בִּיתָן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：bithan)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:5\">EST 1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth7:7\">EST 7:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth7:8\">EST 7:8</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：הֵיכָל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：heykal)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:1\">1KI 21:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:18\">2KI 20:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:7\">2CH 36:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:14\">EZR 4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:9\">PSA 45:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:16\">PSA 45:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:12\">PSA 144:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:28\">PRO 30:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:22\">ISA 13:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa39:7\">ISA 39:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:4\">DAN 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:1\">DAN 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:26\">DAN 4:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel4:5\">JOL 4:5</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Aramaic</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">兰：הֵיכַל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：heykal)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:14\">EZR 4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:1\">DAN 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:26\">DAN 4:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:5\">DAN 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:19\">DAN 6:19</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：αὐλή</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：aulē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc11:46\">1MA 11:46</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：βασιλεία, βασίλειον, βασίλειος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：basileia, basileion, basileios)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:25\">LUK 7:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EpJer1:58\">LJE 1:58</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc2:10\">1MA 2:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：οἶκος, βασιλεία, βασιλεύς</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：oiko (basileias), oikos (basileōs))</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:8\">MAT 11:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt2:1\">JDT 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt2:18\">JDT 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt11:23\">JDT 11:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt12:13\">JDT 12:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt14:18\">JDT 14:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc7:2\">1MA 7:2</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：πραιτώριον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：praitōrion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:27\">MAT 27:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:16\">MRK 15:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:28\">JHN 18:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:28\">JHN 18:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:33\">JHN 18:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:9\">JHN 19:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:35\">ACT 23:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:13\">PHP 1:13</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/PTZ-0064_palace_model_nt.jpg\" alt=\"新约时代宫殿模型\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">新约时代宫殿模型 (© Ray Pritz by United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>宫殿是君王或统治者的住所。这种住所通常比普通百姓的住宅更大、更豪华。宫殿的结构和建筑材料差别很大。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>“宫殿”可译为“王的家”或“统治者的家”。</p>\n<p>希伯来文<em>’armon</em> 有时指的是王宫内修建有防御工事的部分，或其他防御强化住所；参<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:18\">1KI 16:18</a> 。在这些情况下，最好把它译为“堡垒”或“据点”。另参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.13.3.2 要塞、堡垒、城堡 (fortress, stronghold, castle, citadel, fort)&lt;REALIA:3.13.3.2&gt;</a> 。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:9\">PSA 45:9</a> （《和》45:8）：“象牙宫殿”（“Ivory palaces”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ；另参<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:39\">1KI 22:39</a> ）并不是全部用象牙建造的宫殿，而是用象牙装饰的宫殿；装饰的对象可能是建筑本身或里面的家具（参<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:18\">1KI 10:18</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:15\">AMO 3:15</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos6:4\">AMO 6:4</a> ）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:12\">PSA 144:12</a> ：希伯来文<em>heykal</em> 可以指“王宫”或“圣殿”。一般来说，我们通过上下文，或是根据“上帝的”或“王的”等修饰语，能够确定该词指的是哪一个意思。然而，这个词在本节经文中的意思不确定；有些译本译为“王宫”（“palace”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ），而另一些译本译为“圣殿”（“temple”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New American Bible (1970)\">NAB</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> ）。</p>\n<p>关于福音书中的希腊文<em>praitōrion</em> 指的是耶路撒冷城内的哪个建筑，学者们的看法不一。可能是指位于城市西边的希律王宫，也可能是指圣殿区域西北部的安东尼亚堡。位于凯撒利亚的<em>praitōrion</em> （<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:35\">ACT 23:35</a> ）是大希律建造的王宫。在福音书中，把<em>praitōrion</em> 译为“总督官邸”或“统治者居住的大宅”就可以了。在有些语言中，“宫殿”一词可能指军事要塞，非常符合这些新约经文的语境。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
